{
  "stem": "2581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we stayed there until I heard that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother's brother's wife survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she's in Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I went by foot from Munich to Landsberg.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] And in Landsberg, we stayed with our aunt for a while till, you know, I met-- I met my wife.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in a very short time, we wrote an engagement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Orthodox way, because that's the way she wanted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and we got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got married in 1946.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "April 2, 1946.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Well, at least that began my life again, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I started to live again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a very devoted wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I kept saying, this is the kind of girl that my parents would want, they want me to marry, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- we did have-- we have a very good life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had brought up two children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and now, when we had the children and the children got married, and-- I'm skipping all those difficulties during the years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When it came around a holiday, and I was cursing, cursing, why do have-- do-- can do-- have to-- do we have to be alone without having any relatives to share with us a holiday, especially for the young children?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I saw families, I was never envious or jealous about anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I used to see people having families or talking about their brothers and uncles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they have fights with this one and that one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is what I was so envious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would have given anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this is something that you can't turn back the clock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was taken from us in such a brutal way at such a young stage in life-- young age in life.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
